{% comment %}
  WORLD ORDER — wo-about-content.liquid
  About page — chaos animation, approved manifesto copy, Pain/Power/Peace sequence
  All styles live in wo-theme.css. No inline overrides needed.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="wo-about-hero">
  <div class="wo-about-hero__coords">
    <span>38.9764&#xB0; N</span><span>76.4896&#xB0; W</span>
  </div>

  <h1 class="wo-chaos-headline" aria-label="chaos repeats until meaning appears">
    <span class="wo-chaos-line">chaos</span>
    <span class="wo-chaos-line">
      <span class="wo-repeat-roller" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="wo-repeat-strip">
          <span>repeats</span>
          <span>returns</span>
          <span>remains</span>
          <span>repeats</span>
        </span>
      </span>
    </span>
    <span class="wo-chaos-line">until meaning</span>
    <span class="wo-chaos-line"><span class="wo-appear-word">appears.</span></span>
  </h1>

  <ul class="wo-manifesto-lines">
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">I.</span>
      <span><em>Friction over comfort. Signal over noise.</em></span>
    </li>
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">II.</span>
      <span>The world runs on a managed lie &#x2014; social media, advertising, trends &#x2014; a system built to keep the individual dumb, distracted, and dependent. Some comply. <em>Most don&#x27;t notice.</em></span>
    </li>
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">III.</span>
      <span><em>World Order is for those who noticed.</em></span>
    </li>
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">IV.</span>
      <span>To wear this brand is not a statement of style. It is a declaration of sovereignty &#x2014; the conscious acceptance of social exile over silent surrender. <em>The friction is the point. The edge is not anger. It is clarity.</em></span>
    </li>
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">V.</span>
      <span>We call the fear they install in you noise. <em>The signal is what remains when the noise is gone.</em></span>
    </li>
    <li class="wo-manifesto-lines__item">
      <span class="wo-manifesto-lines__num">VI.</span>
      <span>The journey doesn&#x27;t begin in peace. It begins in fire &#x2014; resentment as resistance, sharpness as survival. From that fire comes power. From power, earned through the work, comes <em>the only peace worth having.</em></span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="wo-sequence">
    <div class="wo-sequence__step">
      <div class="wo-sequence__arrow" aria-hidden="true" style="visibility: hidden;">&#x2192;</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__word">Pain</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__desc">Resentment<br>as resistance</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wo-sequence__step">
      <div class="wo-sequence__arrow">&#x2192;</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__word">Power</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__desc">Earned<br>through the work</div>
    </div>
    <div class="wo-sequence__step">
      <div class="wo-sequence__arrow">&#x2192;</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__word">Peace</div>
      <div class="wo-sequence__desc">The only kind<br>worth having</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wo-about-close">
  <blockquote class="wo-about-close__line">Not a slogan. A sequence.</blockquote>
  <div class="wo-never-numb">never.<br>numb.<br>again.</div>
</div>

<script>
(function() {
  function triggerAppear() {
    var el = document.querySelector('.wo-appear-word');
    if (el) setTimeout(function() { el.classList.add('is-visible'); }, 1800);
  }
  if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', triggerAppear);
  } else {
    triggerAppear();
  }
})();
</script>

{% schema %}{"name":"WO About","tag":"div","settings":[],"presets":[{"name":"WO About"}]}{% endschema %}
